Light Properties

Light is an electromagnetic wave that can travel through a vacuum. It does not
require a medium for propagation.

Properties
    Frequency: 400 THz to 790 THz (visible spectrum)
    Speed: 299,792,458 m/s in vacuum (c)
    Wave Type: Electromagnetic, transverse wave
    Dual Nature: Both wave and particle (photon)

Applications
    Vision, photography, fiber optics, lasers

